</ul>
<h1 id="toc6"><span>Political</span></h1>
<p>These code phrases are only used if the parathreat was created or is being fielded by the government organization in question.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Andromeda:</strong> Islamic Republic of Iran.
<ul>
<li><em>Andromeda Sesame:</em> <a href="/oria-hub">Office For The Reclamation of Islamic Artifacts</a>.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Aurora:</strong> Former Empire of Japan.
<ul>
<li><em>Aurora Glory:</em> <a href="/ijamea-hub">Imperial Japanese Anomalous Matters Examination Agency</a> (defunct).</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Flanders:</strong> Relating to the dreamscape constructs of <a href="/oneiroi">the Oneiroi.</a>
<ul>
<li><em>Flanders Fever:</em> <a href="/oneiroi">Oneiroi Collective.</a></li>
<li><em>Flanders Lucid:</em> Oneiroi West.</li>
